Klantcases_hoofdfoto_e1bc7461e0","thumbnail_Klantcases_hoofdfoto.jpg",7.98,245,96,"Klantcases_hoofdfoto_e1bc7461e0",528.5,"https://incredible-beef-2a6059b946.media.strapiapp.com/Klantcases_hoofdfoto_e1bc7461e0.jpg","strapi-provider-upload-strapi-cloud","2023-08-22T10:30:41.119Z","rv3xeudhtoc8d718c1zpq96a","2026-01-05T12:38:34.018Z","hero.primary",{"id":61,"title":62,"asideText":10,"underline":16,"centered":16,"blankAside":16,"aside":63,"content":64,"introductionText":10,"__component":65},2011,"Ben je op zoek naar een IT-expert die direct kan inspringen op een korte opdracht? ","![Afb korte opdrachten wit.jpg](https://incredible-beef-2a6059b946.media.strapiapp.com/Afb_korte_opdrachten_wit_f019dfc9e5.jpg)","ShareValue heeft IT-experts die wij direct beschikbaar kunnen maken voor opdrachten op het gebied van Azure, Microsoft 365, Power Platform en Development. Of je nu behoefte hebt aan advies, een second opinion of de uitvoering van specifieke taken, onze experts bieden snelle en effectieve ondersteuning zonder langdurige contracten. Dit geldt zowel voor grote organisaties en overheidsinstanties als voor het MKB.\n\nWe kijken graag samen met jou waar de behoefte ligt, welke IT-expert het beste past en welke kosten daarbij horen. We bieden zowel uurtarieven als strippenkaarten aan, zodat we flexibel maatwerk kunnen leveren en snel kunnen inspelen op jouw wensen.\n","global.pagesection",{"id":67,"title":68,"subTitle":10,"content":69,"callToActionText":10,"callToActionLink":10,"colorStyle":70,"showAsides":16,"imageUrl":71,"__component":107},65,"Azure","Ons team van ervaren Azure-specialisten is snel inzetbaar voor korte opdrachten. Of je nu een uitgebreide review nodig hebt van je huidige Azure-inrichting, een evaluatie van de Intune-omgeving, een second opinion zoekt of een brainstormsessie wilt voor ruggespraak, wij staan voor je klaar. Onze experts bieden daarnaast eerstelijns beheer voor je servicedesk, helpen bij het opzetten van Infrastructure as Code, zoals met Bicep, en verzorgen ook basistrainingen. Uiteraard wordt alles uitgevoerd volgens de laatste security best practices, zodat je organisatie optimaal beveiligd blijft.","Sugar Glaze",{"id":72,"name":73,"alternativeText":10,"caption":10,"width":74,"height":75,"formats":76,"hash":102,"ext":24,"mime":27,"size":103,"url":104,"previewUrl":10,"provider":55,"provider_metadata":10,"createdAt":105,"updatedAt":105,"documentId":106,"publishedAt":58,"focalPoint":10},823,"afb Azure.jpg",1280,850,{"large":77,"small":83,"medium":89,"thumbnail":95},{"ext":24,"url":78,"hash":79,"mime":27,"name":80,"path":10,"size":81,"width":21,"height":82},"https://incredible-beef-2a6059b946.media.strapiapp.com/large_afb_Azure_74a73ed064.jpg","large_afb_Azure_74a73ed064","large_afb Azure.jpg",246.61,664,{"ext":24,"url":84,"hash":85,"mime":27,"name":86,"path":10,"size":87,"width":36,"height":88},"https://incredible-beef-2a6059b946.media.strapiapp.com/small_afb_Azure_74a73ed064.jpg","small_afb_Azure_74a73ed064","small_afb Azure.jpg",69.57,332,{"ext":24,"url":90,"hash":91,"mime":27,"name":92,"path":10,"size":93,"width":43,"height":94},"https://incredible-beef-2a6059b946.media.strapiapp.com/medium_afb_Azure_74a73ed064.jpg","medium_afb_Azure_74a73ed064","medium_afb Azure.jpg",149.51,498,{"ext":24,"url":96,"hash":97,"mime":27,"name":98,"path":10,"size":99,"width":100,"height":101},"https://incredible-beef-2a6059b946.media.strapiapp.com/thumbnail_afb_Azure_74a73ed064.jpg","thumbnail_afb_Azure_74a73ed064","thumbnail_afb Azure.jpg",15.74,235,156,"afb_Azure_74a73ed064",374.88,"https://incredible-beef-2a6059b946.media.strapiapp.com/afb_Azure_74a73ed064.jpg","2024-09-30T09:27:29.613Z","gun8vbwl18xjetio61qw72a9","global.alternating-page-section",{"id":109,"title":110,"subTitle":10,"content":111,"callToActionText":10,"callToActionLink":10,"colorStyle":112,"showAsides":16,"imageUrl":113,"__component":107},66,"Microsoft 365","Onze specialisten op het gebied van Microsoft 365 kunnen je snel ondersteunen met uiteenlopende korte opdrachten. Wij bieden de juiste oplossing voor bijvoorbeeld advies over de adoptie van M365 of een diepgaande security check. Daarnaast geven we strategisch advies voor M365 en Copilot-implementaties, en ondersteunen we bij Teams Rooms & Telefonie. Wij organiseren workshops en inspiratiesessies om je up-to-date te houden op het gebied van M365, Azure en security, en bieden ook basistrainingen en floorwalking aan om de overgang soepel te laten verlopen.","White",{"id":114,"name":115,"alternativeText":10,"caption":10,"width":74,"height":75,"formats":116,"hash":137,"ext":24,"mime":27,"size":138,"url":139,"previewUrl":10,"provider":55,"provider_metadata":10,"createdAt":140,"updatedAt":140,"documentId":141,"publishedAt":58,"focalPoint":10},821,"afb M365.jpg",{"large":117,"small":122,"medium":127,"thumbnail":132},{"ext":24,"url":118,"hash":119,"mime":27,"name":120,"path":10,"size":121,"width":21,"height":82},"https://incredible-beef-2a6059b946.media.strapiapp.com/large_afb_M365_43dab48b1e.jpg","large_afb_M365_43dab48b1e","large_afb M365.jpg",198.92,{"ext":24,"url":123,"hash":124,"mime":27,"name":125,"path":10,"size":126,"width":36,"height":88},"https://incredible-beef-2a6059b946.media.strapiapp.com/small_afb_M365_43dab48b1e.jpg","small_afb_M365_43dab48b1e","small_afb M365.jpg",59.76,{"ext":24,"url":128,"hash":129,"mime":27,"name":130,"path":10,"size":131,"width":43,"height":94},"https://incredible-beef-2a6059b946.media.strapiapp.com/medium_afb_M365_43dab48b1e.jpg","medium_afb_M365_43dab48b1e","medium_afb M365.jpg",122.64,{"ext":24,"url":133,"hash":134,"mime":27,"name":135,"path":10,"size":136,"width":100,"height":101},"https://incredible-beef-2a6059b946.media.strapiapp.com/thumbnail_afb_M365_43dab48b1e.jpg","thumbnail_afb_M365_43dab48b1e","thumbnail_afb M365.jpg",14,"afb_M365_43dab48b1e",298.15,"https://incredible-beef-2a6059b946.media.strapiapp.com/afb_M365_43dab48b1e.jpg","2024-09-30T09:27:27.249Z","a7ckfhernc1a8pyxj86hnmu2",{"id":143,"title":144,"subTitle":10,"content":145,"callToActionText":10,"callToActionLink":10,"colorStyle":70,"showAsides":16,"imageUrl":146,"__component":107},67,"Power Platform","Heb je directe ondersteuning nodig bij het Power Platform? Onze experts staan klaar om snel bij te springen. Wij bieden advies op maat, of het nu gaat om het ontwikkelen van een Power Platform-app of een uitgebreide security check. We kunnen ook meedenken tijdens ruggespraak- of brainstormsessies en je team ter plaatse begeleiden, zodat zij zelf kunnen leren ontwikkelen. Samen bouwen we aan oplossingen via co-creatie.",{"id":147,"name":148,"alternativeText":10,"caption":10,"width":74,"height":75,"formats":149,"hash":170,"ext":24,"mime":27,"size":171,"url":172,"previewUrl":10,"provider":55,"provider_metadata":10,"createdAt":173,"updatedAt":173,"documentId":174,"publishedAt":58,"focalPoint":10},822,"afb Power Platform.jpg",{"large":150,"small":155,"medium":160,"thumbnail":165},{"ext":24,"url":151,"hash":152,"mime":27,"name":153,"path":10,"size":154,"width":21,"height":82},"https://incredible-beef-2a6059b946.media.strapiapp.com/large_afb_Power_Platform_ceb2683c2f.jpg","large_afb_Power_Platform_ceb2683c2f","large_afb Power Platform.jpg",208.02,{"ext":24,"url":156,"hash":157,"mime":27,"name":158,"path":10,"size":159,"width":36,"height":88},"https://incredible-beef-2a6059b946.media.strapiapp.com/small_afb_Power_Platform_ceb2683c2f.jpg","small_afb_Power_Platform_ceb2683c2f","small_afb Power Platform.jpg",66.01,{"ext":24,"url":161,"hash":162,"mime":27,"name":163,"path":10,"size":164,"width":43,"height":94},"https://incredible-beef-2a6059b946.media.strapiapp.com/medium_afb_Power_Platform_ceb2683c2f.jpg","medium_afb_Power_Platform_ceb2683c2f","medium_afb Power Platform.jpg",131.84,{"ext":24,"url":166,"hash":167,"mime":27,"name":168,"path":10,"size":169,"width":100,"height":101},"https://incredible-beef-2a6059b946.media.strapiapp.com/thumbnail_afb_Power_Platform_ceb2683c2f.jpg","thumbnail_afb_Power_Platform_ceb2683c2f","thumbnail_afb Power Platform.jpg",17.35,"afb_Power_Platform_ceb2683c2f",304.58,"https://incredible-beef-2a6059b946.media.strapiapp.com/afb_Power_Platform_ceb2683c2f.jpg","2024-09-30T09:27:28.295Z","uuqan6p2givkrop4w8ftiq6v",{"id":176,"title":177,"subTitle":10,"content":178,"callToActionText":10,"callToActionLink":10,"colorStyle":112,"showAsides":16,"imageUrl":179,"__component":107},68,"Development","Wanneer je op zoek bent naar ondersteuning voor development-projecten, kun je vertrouwen op onze uitgebreide expertise. \nWij bieden maatwerk, van advies over back-end architectuur en begeleiding bij .NET-migraties tot het opzetten van CI/CD pipelines. \nOnze specialisten helpen o.a. ook bij het kiezen van het juiste framework voor je project, optimaliseren de accessibility van je webapplicatie, en voeren performance reviews uit. \nOf je nu een nieuw project start of extra hulp nodig hebt, wij staan klaar om te helpen.",{"id":180,"name":181,"alternativeText":10,"caption":10,"width":74,"height":75,"formats":182,"hash":203,"ext":24,"mime":27,"size":204,"url":205,"previewUrl":10,"provider":55,"provider_metadata":10,"createdAt":206,"updatedAt":206,"documentId":207,"publishedAt":58,"focalPoint":10},824,"afb NET.jpg",{"large":183,"small":188,"medium":193,"thumbnail":198},{"ext":24,"url":184,"hash":185,"mime":27,"name":186,"path":10,"size":187,"width":21,"height":82},"https://incredible-beef-2a6059b946.media.strapiapp.com/large_afb_NET_304872b058.jpg","large_afb_NET_304872b058","large_afb NET.jpg",294.07,{"ext":24,"url":189,"hash":190,"mime":27,"name":191,"path":10,"size":192,"width":36,"height":88},"https://incredible-beef-2a6059b946.media.strapiapp.com/small_afb_NET_304872b058.jpg","small_afb_NET_304872b058","small_afb NET.jpg",78.27,{"ext":24,"url":194,"hash":195,"mime":27,"name":196,"path":10,"size":197,"width":43,"height":94},"https://incredible-beef-2a6059b946.media.strapiapp.com/medium_afb_NET_304872b058.jpg","medium_afb_NET_304872b058","medium_afb NET.jpg",176.07,{"ext":24,"url":199